---
title: Caesar-Style Chicken & Bacon Burger with Oregano Wedges, Caramelised Onion & Peppercorn Mayo
description: Bring on the weekend with a show-stopping, mouth-watering Dijon-Parmesan sauce and caramelised bacon-topped chicken
burger. And don't overlook the chunky potato wedges. It's bound to become a part of your warmer weather repertoire!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caesar-style-chicken-bacon-burger-d4f46f4b.jpg
